### 2. Runtime Services Consolidation

To resolve circular dependencies cleanly under Clean Architecture, runtime utilities will consume use cases dynamically.

#### [MODIFY] [telegramService.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/services/telegramService.js)
- Replace direct `Booking` document updates and inline socket broadcasts inside `callback_query` query handler with a dynamic import of `acceptBookingUseCase` from the booking module container.
- This automatically executes state transitions, validation checks, clears reminder timers, and dispatches real-time socket events natively.

#### [MODIFY] [socketService.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/services/socketService.js)
- Replace direct Mongoose query `Chat.create()` inside `chat:message` event with a dynamic import and invocation of `persistChatMessageUseCase` from the chat module container.

